entries.journal_entry_description: The Mother Queen is the source of the Urnsor'is infestation. Chief Kallaarac has requested that you kill her. Only then will the Myyydril Tribe be at peace.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to the Deep Depths and defeat the Mother Queen.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Chief Kallaarac in the Myyydril village.
